</i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://libraries.mit.edu/archives/research/collections/collections-ac/ac533.html\">Black Women in the Academy: Defending Our Name, 1894-1994</a>, Conference Records, AC 533. Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Institute Archives and Special Collections, Cambridge, MA.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Globe_Guinier-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Globe_Guinier_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Dembner, Alice (January 14, 1994). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://secure.pqarchiver.com/boston/doc/403571251.html\">\"Guinier cites vacancy of key civil rights post\"</a>. <i>The Boston Globe</i>. Boston, MA<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">January 23,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Boston+Globe&amp;rft.atitle=Guinier+cites+vacancy+of+key+civil+rights+post&amp;rft.date=1994-01-14&amp;rft.aulast=Dembner&amp;rft.aufirst=Alice&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.pqarchiver.com%2Fboston%2Fdoc%2F403571251.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlack+Women+in+the+Academy%3A+Defending+Our+Name+1894-1994\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Tech_Davis-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Tech_Davis_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Shrivastava, Rishi (January 19, 1994). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://tech.mit.edu/V113/N65/women.65n.html\">\"Davis Discusses Issues Concerning Black Women\"</a>. <i>The Tech</i>. Cambridge, MA<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">January 23,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx